               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3r-123v)
 -
                     Homily by ʾabuna Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 66rb l.7–68rb
                     l.23)
 - Homily by St Jacob of Serug on funeral of priests and deacons
                     (fols. 75ra l.2–78rb l.5)
 - Antiphons (ʾaryām, mawāśǝʾt, mǝlṭān, etc.)
                     performed for the funeral of different categories of Christians (fols. 120ra
                     l.17–122rb l.22)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
